### 🧠 How to add more questions in the future:
If you want to add a third or fourth phrase later, just find line **128** in the code (`const questions = [ ... ]`) and paste a new block like this right inside the list:
```javascript
{
    portuguese: "O gato está dormindo.",
    words: ["sleeping", "cat", "is", "the"],
    correctOrder: ["the", "cat", "is", "sleeping"]
}
